Description: A set of extensions for the 'ergm' package to fit weighted networks whose edge weights are ranks. See Krivitsky and Butts (2017) <doi:10.1177/0081175017692623> and Krivitsky, Hunter, Morris, and Klumb (2021) <arXiv:2106.04997>.
